Title: 🚀 [ICO] GGRocket is the first tri-function blockchain gaming protocol.
Body: Hello. I wanted to ask about video recognition. How it's going to work?

Author: GGrocket
Title: 🚀 [ICO] GGRocket is the first tri-function blockchain gaming protocol.
Body: The seller sends a link with the trade video stream to a video recognition server, where it is processed and turned into a smart contract readable information packet and stores it on the blockchain. The smart contract pulls the data from the blockchain, identifies the trade and releases the funds 24 hours after both trade parties are satisfied, or the juries have resolved a dispute.  And GGGuard will be dealing with this data as an escrow system born from the integration of a video recognition algorithm, a system of game API interaction and a bot that decides if the deal has been fulfilled in game.  In a few words. Better read our short article https://medium.com/@GGRocket/video-recognition-how-we-use-it-to-make-our-escrow-better-for-games-5111ce91e9b

Author: cloudgin
Title: 🚀 [ICO] GGRocket is the first tri-function blockchain gaming protocol.
Body: Hello, I would like to find out how to become a jury. What should a user do, how are they selected? Thanks.

Author: GGrocket
Title: 🚀 [ICO] GGRocket is the first tri-function blockchain gaming protocol.
Body: The GG ecosystem randomly selects 5 members of the jury pool and sends the data regarding the deal. Juries analyze the case and come to a conclusion:  ● Was there any type of fraud involved ● How much GGR should be transferred and to each party  Every user with a rating of 2.8 and above will have an option to enter the Jury pool. The rating system for juries implemented in order to build trust for the community and build recognition system for the most active and valuable people in the community. All juries will be working with transaction information and hence will have to sign an online NDA, that they will not share information about the deal with any third party. Juries will be rewarded with GGR for every case they dispute

Title: 🚀 [ICO] GGRocket is the first tri-function blockchain gaming protocol.

The rating will be a multiplication factor when the user earns GGR for feeding the GG Robot with data.  For example A user with rating 2.8 will earn 2.8* normal amount of GGR. Every undisputed exchange will increase the user rating by 0.01 Every successful data feed to the GG Robot will increase the user rating by 0.01 If a user is found fraudulent in an exchange, their rating will decrease by (0.03 + rating*0.01)

Author: AmpaLex11
Title: 🚀 [ICO] GGRocket is the first tri-function blockchain gaming protocol.
Body: Hello  It is expected that the number of games available online, including games supporting online multiplayer, will be growing due to the positive trends in living standards. For the same reason more people will own gaming devices. For example, high-speed internet becomes available more globally allowing gamers to download more games and boost their positive experience.  Current trends in gaming development support players in their willingness to pay for premium/ high-quality content and cosmetics/skins and development of mechanics that encourage gamers to communicate and build communities within games.  The global trend of two-way business - consumer communication allows companies to stay flexible and more concurrent to the need of their customers by customising products to their needs.  The GGRocket blockchain ecosystem will change how the gaming marketplaces work and will open the doors for direct advertising for in-game goods and services. People from all around the world will be able to sell and buy exactly what is needed and at the time when it is needed. We will be able to build a truly decentralised market of needed goods and services for those, who enjoy gaming.

Title: 🚀 [ICO] GGRocket is the first tri-function blockchain gaming protocol.
Body: The GG ecosystem randomly selects 5 members of the jury pool and sends the data regarding the deal. Juries analyze the case and come to a conclusion:  ● Was there any type of fraud involved ● How much GGR should be transferred and to each party  Every user with a rating of 2.8 and above will have an option to enter the Jury pool. The rating system for juries implemented in order to build trust for the community and build recognition system for the most active and valuable people in the community. Juries will be rewarded with GGR for every case they dispute.

You can read more info about them in our WP https://ggrocket.io/wp/GGRocket_Whitepaper_en.pdf?v=20180705134115 Page 18

Author: blithelymorelT6
Title: 🚀 [ICO] GGRocket is the first tri-function blockchain gaming protocol.
Body: I got a question. With GG Ecosystem, when I got my user ID, is there any personal information is going to be stored there?

Author: AmpaLex11
Title: 🚀 [ICO] GGRocket is the first tri-function blockchain gaming protocol.
Body: No, there won't be any personal information stored.  Every ID will be linked to any trade information in the ecosystem and to the information users feed the GG Robot. The ID will be bringing together all the important data, that moves through the system.  ID will attach: 1) Exchange information (API and Video recognition data) 2) GG Rating 3) Data that was fed to the Robot  With the introduction of the ID on the blockchain, we will be able to analyse the interconnected trade information of buyers and sellers. Consequently, the GG Robot will have more data to handle, hence, improving the machine learning algorithm.  All data that is transferred to the smart contract is stored on the blockchain and pegged to the ID’s of the seller and buyer. The data is obfuscated from the users in game credentials. We will only store trade data and peg to the ID.

Title: 🚀 [ICO] GGRocket is the first tri-function blockchain gaming protocol.
Body: why do you need blockchain?

Author: AmpaLex11
Title: 🚀 [ICO] GGRocket is the first tri-function blockchain gaming protocol.
Body: At the heart of every self-sustaining project in the blockchain industry lies the principles of commission reduction, decentralization, identity anonymity and an idea of a fairer society. The introduction of smart contracts has allowed for an absolutely new system of a trustless bargain interaction. Consequently, the costs for escrow have dropped from 5-15% to 0.1-1%.

Author: AmpaLex11
Title: 🚀 [ICO] GGRocket is the first tri-function blockchain gaming protocol.
Body: Prior to blockchain introduction if we wanted to track our customers from all various platforms we needed access to our partners' google analytics (or alternatives), download the data and synchronize it with our database. In theory, it is hard but possible. In practice no business would allow us full access to their analytical data. On the other hand, the key blockchain functional is information storage and network elements synchronization, thus we can obtain the needed data without intruding business or individual privacy.

Author: AmpaLex11
Title: 🚀 [ICO] GGRocket is the first tri-function blockchain gaming protocol.
Body: The GG Rocket project has been evolving for over two years and has turned from a marketplace for gamers, into a high tech company, that uses data analysis and machine learning technologies to produce high-quality target advertisement.  We have analyzed the blockchain industry and decided that blockchain can be the heart of the GG Rocket ecosystem. Blockchain will bring user's, information, video recognition as a part of machine learning process, all together and increase the productivity of our system to a previously unreachable level. Moreover, users - the most critical part of any decentralized project (and we aim to be one) - will be able to benefit from their interaction with the system directly through GGT.  So, the idea was evolving over time as we developed our own gaming marketplace.

Author: AmpaLex11
Title: 🚀 [ICO] GGRocket is the first tri-function blockchain gaming protocol.
Body: We begin #GGRocket #AMA #sessions with our team members. First one is Alexey our CEO. 😎  VIDEO: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GY_oArw9DlA  From the youngest years, Alexey was fond of video games. RPG genre is his favorite. The whole story of in-game trading and the idea to create GGRocket began with e-Sports.  As a professional World of Warcraft player, Alexey was among the best PvP players in the world with his famous team, fans, and streams. But over the time the idea of creating something for gamers and e-sport players as himself came up. That time he was studying in prestigious Gubkin Russian State University of Oil and Gas. It was clear, that in the future there will be a profitable and prestigious job in the oil business, but Alexey still dreamt about his passion - video games.  “Why make money on a prestigious job, that you don’t like if you can transform your hobby into your job and make money with what you like and do the best?” - with that in mind, Alexey left the university and founded his first gaming project. To make this possible, he had to sell his car for the first seed capital. In the beginning, there were a lot of difficulties. Small seed, shortage of money and marketing, little experience, etc. But despite all that with all the passion and aspiration put in the project it started to gain profit.  Next 3 years there were three more successful gaming projects Alexey was working on until he found a marketplace for in-game services and trading - Legionfarm.com. In 2017 the marketplace made $1 000 000 annual turnover and revealed a lot of problems in this sphere of business. Working on the project and gaining experience in trading in-game services the team developed an understanding of this field and checked some hypothesis. After analyzing market situation and the results of the trading experience of Legionfarm.com the decision of creating a next-generation trading platform was made. We call it GGRocket 🚀  🚀GGRocket - blockchain platform for in-game trading. For more information, please visit https://ggrocket.io/en  Join our GGRocket Token-sale Telegram channel and other social media for all the important news and notes:  📢 Telegram: https://goo.gl/jkSSS6 🔸 BitcoinTalk: https://goo.gl/u4kAYW 🔸 Facebook: https://goo.gl/cohy2Z 🔸 Twitter: https://goo.gl/KVb6Zc 🔸 Medium: https://goo.gl/KMmSZK 🔸 Instagram: https://goo.gl/zwJ773 🔸 LinkedIn: https://goo.gl/PPXun1

Author: AmpaLex11
Title: 🚀 [ICO] GGRocket is the first tri-function blockchain gaming protocol.
Body: 🙀HACKATHON OR OUR PROGRAMMERS WORKING 26 HOURS WITHOUT A BREAK  🉐 This post will help you found out the core aim of our team’s trip to Hong Kong and what was happening to our guys.  So the main goal was taking part in such interesting forum as Hackathon. What’s that?  So it’s a place where a lot of teams of developers take part and create any product from the very beginning. And our guys were working without any sleep or breaks🙈  As for us, the product was a smart-contract for GGRocket escrow service which allows to look through the terms of a deal and make a decision whether this deal was legitimate and if the service could take the money back if necessary. It’s in a few words.  🚀 As a result, our guys managed to create already operating smart-contract which is now being integrated into our MVP.  Unfortunately, we didn’t take the first prize but it was a great experience for us. It was essential to get a feedback from influential people in the sphere of blockchain gaming. Author: AmpaLex11
Title: 🚀 [ICO] GGRocket is the first tri-function blockchain gaming protocol.
Body: WE HAVE SOME GREAT NEWS  Last week we met with 19 leaders of the World of Warcraft gaming teams and guilds to talk with them about their problems with payment systems and cash flows. The result of the interview was the following: transaction costs average 24% of the total turnover of the team, while the turnover varies from 27 to 70 thousand dollars, depending on the number of participants.  At the start, our solution will allow PRO-teams of our platform to withhold spending on financial flows of within 3-5 percent, receive payments in the cryptocurrency, and automatically redistribute funds between team members. 16 of 19 interviews resulted in an agreement on connecting teams to the GGRocket payment solution.  All 16 guilds will soon be connected to our system and receive an escrow service with the ability to accept payments from customers and convert fees to GGT, which is currently the domestic currency of our platform. In the period until GGT appears on the crypto-exchange exchanges, GGT can be exchanged for bitcoin or ether when the currency is withdrawn from the platform, as well as transferred to other platform participants / redistributed among the members of their team.  The total annual turnover from the sale of training services and in-game values among surveyed guilds is $ 10.7 million for the year 2017. Together with the release of a large-scale renovation of WoW in August 2018, their turnover is projected to increase to $ 20 million in 2018. And this is only a few percents of the total trading volume in the in-game market.  Visit our website to learn more about PRO-teams problems and solutions.
